SECTION 1. The following sitios in the Municipality of Macrohon, Province of Leyte, are constituted or converted into distinct and independent barrios of said municipality, to wit:

The sitios of Laray, Abag and Pananawan to be known as the barrio of Laray;

The sitios of Sindañgan Proper, Guinabonan, Danao, Gawisan and Lunang to be known as the barrio of Sindañgan;

The sitio of Rizal to be known as the barrio of Rizal ;

The sitio of Mohon to be known as the barrio of Mohon;

The sitios of Camboro Proper, Malico, Ad, Magtubod, Coge, and Tabunan to be known as the barrio of Camboro;

The sitios of Mangmang Proper, Coot, Abag, Bagacay; Pong-on and Lundag

The sitio of Buscayan to be known as the barrio of Buscayan;

The sitio of Canlusay to be known as the barrio of Canlusay;

The sitios of Malopolo, Cacawan and Salumbañgon to be known as the barrio of Malopolo; and

The sitios of Mabini and Pajo to be known as the barrio of Mabini.

SEC. 2. The following sitios in the Municipality of St. Bernard, Province of Leyte, are converted into barrios of said municipality, to wit:

The sitio of Tabontabon to be known as the barrio of Tabontabon;

The sitio of Bantawon to be known as the barrio of Bantawon;

